*Zaboravite* odlazak u školu (Forget about going to school).
*Niko ne bi trebao da *zaboravi* njegovu istoriju (Nobody should forget his history).
*Da *zaboravimo* naše probleme (Let's forget our problems).
*On se *zaboravio* da plati račun (He forgot to pay the bill).
*Moraš da *zaboraviš* sve što si čuo (You have to forget everything you heard).